data.description: Welcome to 8408 Grand Trevi Dr in The Fountains.  This stunning two bedroom and two bath condo has been meticulously maintained and is turnkey.  Newer luxury vinyl plank flooring and new carpet compliment the fresh paint.  You'll be hard pressed to find a more comfortable and cozy condo.  The living rooms soaring ceiling, abundance of natural light and electric fireplace will quickly become your favorite room.   You'll enjoy the private deck for relaxing in your oasis.
